title: Milo Manara: Piranese the Prison Planet (Heavy Metal|2002|Pudgy)
description:
Contains:   Piranese - The Prison Planet (2002, 2004) (Pudgy)



             " No one knows if Piranese exists. But Hell is real. It is Piranese,
               the prison planet where all the outcasts of the Empire are held. No
               one escapes and there is only the faintest hope of survival. But now
               this order is disturbed by the appearance of a young woman who has
               avoided the genetic tyranny of the guardians. Will she be the
               liberator that all await? " 

              --  from the back cover
